{"tid":2012601,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(香城online)認真    開花戰術post （幫推唔該）","createTime":"2020-05-11T17:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T14:08:20.000Z","uid":342968,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f257900b2982dce2f7619c372c2a355b7e65ba66","tid":2012601,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"其實由6月到依加 香港都有個問題 <br />\n猶其係依加 個問題越黎越明顯<br />\n<br />\n就係每次行動為左方便手足 <br />\n文宣會公佈開花地點<br />\n所以每次開花 都會引黎一大班狗<br />\n<br />\n所以小弟總結左幾點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.當日提前1個鐘再公佈開花地點</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好處：可以避開重狗地點，因應番當日邊到易打易走，再進行公佈，提高開花成效，減低手足被捕風險</span></span><br />\n*提早一個鐘準備戰場集合，切忌遲到，準時開波！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.狗到左 就轉番街坊裝，再決定下一個目標地點</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好處：敵人在明，手足在暗. 狗每次既行動都需要上級order,明顯機動力係慢過手足，如果識玩可以玩好耐</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3.由於好重要，所以要再講多次</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>唔好遲到</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">壞壞壞處：遲左開波，就等於俾時間狗去部署，過左咁耐，你唔係仲遲到掛</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外有幾點想提番大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">依加和理非都係狗既目標 麻煩大家行動時，無論和理非定前線 麻煩你  <span style=\"color: red;\">全黑</span><span style=\"color: green;\">包臉</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">遮紋身</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原因：依加四圍都係cam，狗會跟據你個外露特徵去上訴你 所以千祈唔好搏 就算係夏天 都要好好保護自己</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">獅鳥完 唔該你同你隊友分散咁急步尻遊，直到你肯定冇可能俾狗跟到你,我自己好鍾意急步行同跑去人群多既地方轉黎轉去，跑過10分鐘先再搵番隊友</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好處：偽裝狗數量有限，跟到一個跟唔到第二個，跟到你 都追唔過你</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下呢三點要留意（就最近幾次行動總結）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.停止屌狗</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原因：講撚到口都臭 由6月起，我肯定至少有10份1既手足 都係俾屌狗既人累撚死   屌狗既人企係後面 狗發癲果陣 跑最快既一定係屌狗果個 前面既手足就瀨撚哂野 我見過好多火魔就係因為俾屌狗既人累死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">準備戰爭思想</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原因；出黎打仗 唔係玩 大家冇野做 可以試吓做哨（報狗數 防被包抄）<span style=\"color: violet;\">母親節果日就係衰在冇人知自己要向邊跑 又冇人知幾時被包抄</span></span></span><br />\n*請善用哨兵tg + <a href=\"https://hkmap.live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HUzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=a286c913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以光復香港為首任，隨時準備出擊</span>"},{"pid":"3478e37014c37a23e56439d813375c9ce0781f2c","tid":2012601,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:41:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8386365af58a39603bdcb768df371bbfe9152345","tid":2012601,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:43:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6d233520be770d52e6924c9f9521a1583539399","tid":2012601,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:43:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07407cf5714d7958bd78a8cc6be2db85824b14fc","tid":2012601,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:43:31.000Z","msg":"幫手 推多幾次"},{"pid":"e0f46497d1d1c8522ee378fb19a3be04ef1a52d2","tid":2012601,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:43:55.000Z","msg":"認真post"},{"pid":"182d36ad7fff913bd483a19b79dc3a07d3829e2f","tid":2012601,"uid":235316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T17:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dP2uWaX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdP2uWaX.jpg&h=28313514&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpT9WaY.jpg\" data-th